## Part 2: Mobile UI Audit Findings

### Critical Mobile Issues Found:
1. **BottomNav Profile hardcoded** to `FragMaster` — not dynamic
2. **No search on mobile** — navbar hides it on small screens with no alternative  
3. **VideoCard thumbnails** too small on narrow screens (need full-width treatment)
4. **Font sizes too small** — tracking-widest at 10px is illegible on phone screens
5. **Upload page** has no mobile-optimized drag-and-drop fallback
6. **Login/Register** pages have poor mobile tab spacing

---

## Part 3: New Design Direction — "Liquid Glass" 

### Design Identity
Inspired by: **YouTube Studio 2025 + Arc Browser + Apple Vision Pro UI**

| Element | Old | New |
|---|---|---|
| **Color Palette** | Obsidian Black + Crimson Red | Deep Slate + Electric Violet + White |
| **Primary Accent** | `#E50914` (Netflix Red) | `#7C3AED` (Electric Violet) |
| **Background** | `#050505` flat black | `#0f0f13` with subtle mesh gradient |
| **Surface** | `#0e0e0e` harsh dark | `#1a1a2e` deep blue-slate |
| **Typography** | Bebas Neue display | **Space Grotesk** (modern, rounded, tech) |
| **Body Font** | Outfit | **Inter** (max readability, system-feel) |
| **Card Style** | Hard square borders | Rounded `rounded-2xl` with glass inner |
| **Borders** | `border-white/5` barely visible | `border-white/8` with gradient top highlight |
| **Buttons** | Capitol letter blocks | Pill-shaped with gradient fills |
| **Icons** | Minimal outline | Filled active states |

### Color Tokens (New)
```css
--color-background: #0f0f13;
--color-surface: #1a1a2e;
--color-surface-2: #252540;
--color-foreground: #f0f0ff;
--color-muted: #6b7280;
--color-primary: #7C3AED;        /* Electric Violet */
--color-primary-hover: #6d28d9;
--color-accent: #06b6d4;         /* Electric Cyan - secondary */
--color-live: #ef4444;           /* Actual live dot */
--color-border: rgba(255,255,255,0.08);
--color-glass: rgba(255,255,255,0.04);
```

