## Part 4: Proposed Changes

### Design System
#### [MODIFY] [globals.css](file:///C:/GOLive/app/globals.css)
- New color palette (violet/cyan/slate)
- New typography (Space Grotesk + Inter from Google Fonts)
- New component classes: `.glass-card`, `.pill-btn`, `.gradient-text`
- Better mobile viewport handling

#### [MODIFY] [layout.tsx](file:///C:/GOLive/app/layout.tsx)
