## Verification Plan

### Automated Tests
1. `npm run build` — confirm 0 TypeScript errors
2. `npx vercel --prod` — deploy to production URL
3. Browser agent tests all pages at mobile viewport (375px)

### Manual Verification
- Load live URL on mobile device and test:
  - Home, Watch, Profile, Upload, Login, Register, Studio pages
  - Bottom nav navigation
  - Search bar on mobile
  - Video play and quality selector
